<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>Letters to the editor</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">September 3, 2004 | Page 4</font></P>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><P><B>OTHER LETTERS BELOW:</B><BR>
